## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources and the lack of empirical data directly from businesses that have implemented universal standards. Additionally, the perspectives gathered are predominantly supportive of universal standards, which may not fully represent dissenting views or the challenges businesses might face in adopting such standards. Further research involving case studies and direct business testimonials would provide a more balanced view.

